  "summary": "Malicious code in rtms-manager (npm)",
  "details": "Package rtms-manager@1.2.0 runs a preinstall hook that captures the installer's entire environment variables (including NPM_TOKEN, GITHUB_TOKEN, CI/CD secrets) via `env | base64` and exfiltrates them to 244ci90mnvztem0dg1g6nuhreik983ws[.]oastify[.]com via HTTP POST. The attacker uses captured credentials for follow-on supply-chain attacks against other packages the victim has publish access to.",
